        <ul>
            <li>Encouraging compliance with POPIA conditions</li>
            <li>Dealing with requests made to the business pursuant to POPIA</li>
            <li>Working with the Information Regulator in relation to investigations</li>
            <li>Ensuring the business complies with POPIA provisions</li>
            <li>Developing and updating the business's Privacy Policy</li>
            <li>Conducting personal information impact assessments</li>
            <li>Maintaining records of all processing operations</li>
        </ul>
        
